@startuml
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam ParticipantPadding 20

actor "Manager" as User
participant "AdminDashboard\n(JS class)" as Dashboard
participant "ApiService\n(JS class)" as ApiService
participant "JwtAuthFilter" as JwtFilter
participant "ManagerController" as Controller
participant "PotentialCustomerServiceImpl" as PotentialService
participant "IBookingRepository" as BookingRepo

== Xem khách hàng tiềm năng ==
User -> Dashboard: 1. Click tab "Khách hàng tiềm năng"
Dashboard -> Dashboard: 2. switchTab() → loadPotentialCustomers()
Dashboard -> ApiService: 3. getPotentialCustomers()
ApiService -> JwtFilter: 4. GET /api/manager/potential-customers
JwtFilter -> JwtFilter: 5. validateToken() + extractRole()
JwtFilter -> Controller: 6. Forward request
Controller -> PotentialService: 7. getPotentialCustomers()
PotentialService -> BookingRepo: 8. findPotentialCustomers()
BookingRepo --> PotentialService: 9. List<Object[]>
PotentialService -> PotentialService: 10. Map sang DTO
PotentialService --> Controller: 11. Response
Controller --> ApiService: 12. 200 OK + JSON
ApiService --> Dashboard: 13. customers[]
Dashboard -> Dashboard: 14. Tính điểm + phân hạng
Dashboard -> Dashboard: 15. Render bảng
Dashboard --> User: 16. Hiển thị danh sách

== Làm mới ==
User -> Dashboard: 17. Click "Làm mới"
Dashboard -> Dashboard: 18. loadPotentialCustomers()
Dashboard --> User: 19. Cập nhật danh sách

@enduml